{"tid":2393663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企有自私撚慘過食屎","createTime":"2021-02-03T15:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T17:31:56.000Z","uid":340137,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8a590c88d6efb104869b2ac7489c6b47ef0e9c69","tid":2393663,"uid":340137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇遇過呢個情況<br />\n就係你哋嘅兄弟姊妹好鍾意帶自己另一半返屋企瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的 我啊哥成日帶佢女朋友返屋企瞓 <br />\n初初開始都係一個星期住一日 無乜嘢搞唔到我<br />\n耐少少本性現形 對兩老無禮貌 招呼都唔打 <br />\n嫌我屋企冇餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我啊哥係典型大男人性格 好要面<br />\n之所以條女會係我屋企肆無忌憚 <br />\n或多或少都係我啊哥縱容 <br />\n因為本身佢對屋企人都好唔尊重<br />\n利申之前打過我老母又打過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而最近佢女朋友係我屋企住撚左兩個禮拜 <br />\n令我好困擾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢女朋友嗰日上嚟屋企已經病病地 <br />\n我老豆媽子好聲好氣建議佢求醫食藥<br />\n仲比埋錢佢去睇<br />\n佢堅持話自己冇事 唔需要去睇醫生<br />\n到後來我老豆都有少少病<br />\n佢哋先坦白講佢哋學校有同學感染肺炎 <br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母明知有肺炎仲返屋企住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問點解唔搵地方隔離 佢哋話冇諗過<br />\n屌咁撚自私都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最唔撚明嘅係當全世界防疫緊 <br />\n想約朋友都唔敢嘅時候<br />\n條女明知自己會有感染可能性都要去人屋企住<br />\n咁都係嘅 感染人哋屋企人點都好過感染自己屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82cfd83b3431f91eb6ff88fc71b189dd53fa55e","tid":2393663,"uid":365977,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"慘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n閲"},{"pid":"afdbbe5d557719ca8a8d8170de823cf48b9b1763","tid":2393663,"uid":220458,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"邊忽大男人<br />\n廢柴一個<br />\n見自己老母比人打唔識一巴車到條臭西跪喺到含撚<br />\n好意思叫大男人？"},{"pid":"f6e8127b263c25979820e59c28ac1b8e5161fe7a","tid":2393663,"uid":109573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:08:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">打過我老母又打過我</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你都忍到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071fdb63d3528ce83ac86abebdf826290568f8a3","tid":2393663,"uid":122516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"大男人唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b493c687bbb3303266abf786d7e13265a2d401","tid":2393663,"uid":140300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"絲打撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好明白你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喱啲男人死撚左去算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a37b98e5eac25d763d0970966d342922ff15f43","tid":2393663,"uid":147071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T15:14:46.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係病緊 過嚟我屋企 <br />\n求照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffacf277b2c385029f03b888b9964921aa7b1ff6","tid":2393663,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T